variables.input:
fetch events
| filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == concat("smoketest_",$Env)
and task.outcome == "Success"
| fields artifact.name
| dedup artifact.name

fetch events
| filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and (event.type == "smoketest_qa" or event.type == "smoketest_prod")
and in(artifact.name, $Application)
and task.outcome == "Success"
| fields artifact.id
| dedup artifact.id

fetch events
| filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and (event.type == "smoketest_qa" or event.type == "smoketest_prod")
and in(artifact.name, $Application)
and task.outcome == "Success"
| fields artifact.version
| dedup artifact.version

0.title: ✈️Successful Prod Runs by App
0.query:
fetch events
| filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "checkout"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
| join on:cicd.pipeline.id, fields:{task.outcome,event.type},kind:leftOuter, [
 fetch events
 | filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "smoketest_prod"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
]
| fieldsAdd value = if(task.outcome == "Success",1,else:0)
| summarize value = sum(value), by:{app=artifact.name}
| fields app, success = value
| sort success desc

1.title: Checkout
1.query:
fetch events
| filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "checkout"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
| join on:cicd.pipeline.id, fields:{task.outcome,event.type},kind:leftOuter,[
 fetch events
 | filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "checkout"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
]
| fieldsAdd value = if(task.outcome == "Success",1,else:0)
| summarize value = avg(value), by:{app=artifact.name}
| fields app, successRate = round(value * 100)
| sort successRate desc

8.title: Latest Release in Production Environment
8.query:
fetch events
| filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "checkout"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
| sort timestamp desc
| join on:cicd.pipeline.id, fields:{task.outcome,event.type, end_time},kind:inner, [
 fetch events
 | filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "smoketest_prod"
and task.outcome == "Success"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
]
| sort timestamp desc
| summarize {
  start_time = takeFirst(start_time),
  end_time = takeFirst(end_time),
  cicd.pipeline.run.id = takeFirst(cicd.pipeline.run.id),
  Build = takeFirst(artifact.id),
  Version = takeFirst(artifact.version)
}, by:{Application = artifact.name}
| fields Application, Version, Build, Time = now() - end_time
| fieldsAdd link = $Link
| fieldsAdd link = replaceString(link,"{{APP}}", Application)
| fieldsAdd link = replaceString(link,"{{ENV}}","prod")

10.title: QA Deployments
10.query:
fetch events
| filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "checkout"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
| join on:cicd.pipeline.id, fields:{task.outcome,event.type, end_time},kind:leftOuter, [
 fetch events
 | filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "smoketest_qa"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
]
| fieldsAdd value = if(task.outcome == "Success",1,else:0)
| maketimeseries sli = avg(value), success = sum(value), total = count()
| fieldsAdd valueSuccess = arraySum(success), valueTotal = arraySum(total)
| fieldsAdd valueSli = toLong($qa_deployment_success_target) / (valueSuccess/valueTotal * 100)

21.title: Smoke Test Objective Validations in QA
21.query:
fetch events
| filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "checkout"
| filter in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
| join on:cicd.pipeline.id, fields:{task.outcome,event.type,cicd.pipeline.run.id},kind:inner, [
 fetch events
 | filter event.kind == "SDLC_EVENT"  
and event.type == "smoketest_qa"
and task.outcome == "Success"
and in(artifact.name,$Application)
and in(artifact.id,$Build)
and in(artifact.version,$Verison)
]
| fieldsAdd id = cicd.pipeline.id, run_id = cicd.pipeline.run.id, app = artifact.name
| join on:{id,run_id, app},prefix:"objective.",kind:inner,[
fetch bizevents 
| filter event.provider == "dynatrace.site.reliability.guardian"
and isNotNull(validation.workflow.trigger_type)
and isNotNull(guardian.variables)
and isNotNull(guardian.objective)
| sort timestamp desc
| parse execution_context,"""JSON:vars"""
| fieldsAdd id = vars[`sdlc_pipeline_id`], run_id = vars[`sdlc_pipeline_run_id`]
| filter isNotNull(id) and isNotNull(run_id)
| parse guardian.objective,"""JSON:obj"""
| fields id, run_id, app = vars[`app`],env = vars[`env`], name = obj[`name`], status = obj[`status`], value = obj[`value`]
| summarize array = collectArray(record(env, name, status,value)), by:{id, run_id, app}
]
| fields app, alias: Application, objective.array
| expand obj = objective.array 
| summarize Objective_Result = avg(toLong(obj[`value`])), by:{Application, Environment = obj[`env`], Objective=obj[`name`], Status = obj[`status`]}

| fields id, run_id, app = vars[`app`],env = vars[`env`], name = obj[`name`], status = obj[`status`], value = obj[`value`]
| summarize sli = avg(toLong(value)), by:{id, run_id, env, app}
] 
| summarize validation = avg(toDouble(objective.sli)),by:{app = objective.app, env = objective.env}

29.content:
# Release Health along the Software Development Lifecycle (SDLC)

This dashboard provides a comprehensive view of release health and progress by tracking key metrics across both QA and production environments. It offers end-to-end visibility into the delivery pipeline - from code checkout to production deployment — enabling teams to monitor performance, validate user impact, and ensure release quality at every stage.

30.content:
### Post-Deployment Validation

This section presents the latest release validation results conducted by the Site Reliability Guardian. These validations ensure that all defined objectives are met before a release advances to the next stage, reinforcing quality, reliability, and security throughout the delivery pipeline.

---

31.content:
### Software Delivery Pipeline

This section offers a comprehensive visualization of the entire software delivery lifecycle — from initial code checkout to final deployment in the production environment. It provides real-time insights into each stage of the pipeline, enabling teams to monitor progress, identify bottlenecks, and optimize delivery efficiency.
